  "text": "We evaluate Faster R-CNN trained on VOC 07 and VOC 07+12 with three different backbones (ResNet50, ResNet101, and ResNeXt101 32x4d [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ). Training with our AP loss gives a consistent improvement (see Tab. 5) and pushes the standard Faster R-CNN very close to state-of-the-art values (≈ 84.1) achieved by significantly more complex architectures [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
